results.name: Restricted growth sequence transform of A290093.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..59049
xref: For all i, j: a(i) = a(j) <=> A290093(n) = A290093(n), thus this matches to all the same base-3 (ternary) related sequences as A290093: A006047, A053735, A062756, A081603, A117942, A206424, A227428, A290091, A290092, A290079, and many others.
